name: 03-Data Profiling and EDA
content:
Data Profiling and Analysis

Data Profiling:

  • Histogram distributions were generated for key features:
  • acct_avl_money_before_amt: Range from -243.09 to 31,253.38
  • acct_cl_amt: Range 0 to 40,000.
  • acct_curr_bal: Range -863.5 to 21,017.96.
  • authzn_amt: Range 0 to 4,400.

Descriptive Analysis:

  • Frequency distributions of balances, credit limits, and transaction sizes.
  • Outlier detection for negative balances and extreme credit limits.

Predictive Analysis:

  • Fraud probability scores assigned per transaction.
  • Aggregated fraud patterns by customer, account type, and transaction size.
  • Visualization of fraud-heavy ranges (e.g., small balances + high authorization amounts).
